OL,6,FThe data desert
OL,8,FThat lack of evidence is a huge part
OL,9,Fof the problem.
OL,11,FIn Wales, there is no consistent
OL,12,Fnational data available on how many
OL,13,Fchildren can read unfamiliar words at
OL,14,Fthe early stages of learning.
