OL,6,FSo when Estyn warns that some schools
OL,7,Fare focusing too narrowly on decoding,
OL,8,Fan obvious question follows: on what
OL,9,Fevidence?
OL,11,FInspectors fill the gap
OL,13,FIn the absence of national data,
OL,14,Finspection evidence now carries
OL,15,Fenormous weight.
OL,17,FEstyn's judgements have become the
OL,18,Fclosest thing Wales has to a national
OL,19,Fpicture of reading standards. What
OL,20,Finspectors praise or criticise can
OL,21,Fquickly shape practice across schools.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
