OL,3,CWales's reading problem ` and the data
OL,4,Cgap behind it
OL,6,FHowever, ITV News has previously found
OL,7,FEstyn inspection reports which appear
OL,8,Fto encourage "cueing", an approach to
OL,9,Fteaching reading that is unsupported
OL,10,Fby evidence.
OL,12,FSimilarly, when giving evidence to a
OL,13,FSenedd committee, Estyn's chief
OL,14,Finspector appeared not to have a firm
OL,15,Fgrasp of how reading is taught,
OL,16,Fconfusing "cueing" with a different,
OL,17,Funrelated practice.
