OL,6,FSome pupils - especially those with
OL,7,Flearning difficulties or with less
OL,8,Fexposure to reading at home - need far
OL,9,Fmore explicit instruction in how this
OL,10,Fworks.
OL,12,FAgainst that backdrop, cautioning that
OL,13,Fschools may be focusing too much on
OL,14,Fdecoding risks adding to the confusion
OL,15,Frather than clearing it up.
