OL,6,FThe bigger picture
OL,8,FNobody sensible denies the importance
OL,9,Fof fostering a love of reading and
OL,10,Frich language experiences in schools,
OL,11,Fparticularly as National Literacy
OL,12,FTrust surveys suggest fewer children
OL,13,Fare reading for enjoyment than ever
OL,14,Fbefore.
OL,16,FBut this report also, inadvertently,
OL,17,Fhighlights a deeper issue.
